title: VA - Music from Plebs mp3 - thatcher
description:
I have put together a collection of music featured in the UK TV show Plebs.

A nice selection of Ska and Reggae.

The Liquidator - Harry J All Stars

Dave & Ansell Collins - Double Barrel

The Upsetters - Return of Django

Funky Kingston - Toots and the Maytals

Baba Brooks - Watermelon Man

lord tanamo - I'm In The Mood For Ska

The Skatalites-Musical Communion

Tommy McCook & The Skatalites - Doctor Zhivago

The Jamaicans - Ba Ba Boom

Rudy Mills - John Jones

Teenage Ska - Baba Brooks band

Toots & the Maytals 54-46 was my number

Thanks to the internet for supplying these tracks!
